quran[26{c,v,t}:
92,15,Laa yaslaahaaa illal ashqaa
92,16,Allazee kazzaba wa tawallaa
92,17,Wa sa yujannnabuhal atqaa
92,18,Allazee yu'tee maalahoo yatazakkaa
92,19,Wa maa li ahadin 'indahoo min ni'matin tujzaaa
92,20,Illab tighaaa'a wajhi rabbihil a 'laa
92,21,Wa lasawfa yardaa
93,1,Wad duhaa
93,2,Wal laili iza sajaa
93,3,Ma wad da'aka rabbuka wa ma qalaa
93,4,Walal-aakhiratu khairul laka minal-oola
93,5,Wa la sawfa y'uteeka rabbuka fatarda
93,6,Alam ya jidka yateeman fa aawaa
93,7,Wa wa jadaka daal lan fahada
93,8,Wa wa jadaka 'aa-ilan fa aghnaa
93,9,Fa am mal yateema fala taqhar
93,10,Wa am mas saa-ila fala tanhar
93,11,Wa amma bi ni'mati rabbika fahad dith
94,1,Alam nashrah laka sadrak
94,2,Wa wa d'ana 'anka wizrak
94,3,Allazee anqada zahrak
94,4,Wa raf 'ana laka zikrak
94,5,Fa inna ma'al usri yusra
94,6,Inna ma'al 'usri yusra
94,7,Fa iza faragh ta fansab
94,8,Wa ilaa rabbika far ghab
